codes.algorithms.dataStructures
A package which lets the users, to implement different functions of data structures to solve problems in other classes.
  • Classes in codes.algorithms.dataStructures used by codes.algorithms.dataStructures
    Class
    Description
    List
    Class List, the super class of LinkedList follows the technique of doubly linked list.
    Queue
    Interface Queue, is implemented in class LinkedList and is used to take in elements from the first index and remove elements from the first index, basically it works on FIFO (First-In-First-Out) technique.
    Stack
    Interface Stack, is implemented in class LinkedList and is used to take in elements from the first index and remove elements from the last index, basically it works on FILO (First-In-Last-Out) technique.
